273
00:24:17,866 --> 00:24:21,266
BUT THERE'S A PROFOUND
DISAGREEMENT BETWEEN THEM.

274
00:24:21,333 --> 00:24:24,066
BECAUSE FOR THEM,
EVEN LIFE AND DEATH ITSELF

275
00:24:24,133 --> 00:24:25,866
MEAN DIFFERENT THINGS.

